# simd_packed_double4

**Type Alias**

A packed vector of four 64-bit floating-point elements.

## Declaration

```swift
typealias simd_packed_double4 = SIMD4<Double>
```

## Alternative Type Alias

- **packed_double4**

## Packed vector data types

- **simd_packed_double2**: A packed vector of two 64-bit floating-point elements.
- **simd_packed_double8**: A packed vector of eight 64-bit floating-point elements.
